column9: Nice school, good facilities. In the future, if I have a child, I will let him study here.
Knowing the TQD side, just visiting the H Binh side is facility 2, seeing a larger yard, a beautiful campus. When there is an open day or conference, I will join.

I used to go to this school to visit to find out for my children to enter later, and found that the SACE curriculum is quite okay so that I can send my children to study abroad in good universities later.
